{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058640/extras/UltimateFlyingExp.png?t=1725272439\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Experience the Thrill of Flight Like Never Before</h2>WaggaSim is a <strong>realistic paragliding simulator</strong> with advanced <strong>soft-body physics</strong>. The wings and wind-socks behave like <strong>real fabric</strong>, bending and flexing naturally. <strong>Design</strong> or modify your <strong>own gear</strong>, fly and perfect your style: soaring, thermaling, acro, freestyle... This is free flying, the opportunities are endless !<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058640/extras/Thermaling.gif?t=1725272439\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2><strong>Realistic Wing Dynamics</strong><br>Experience true-to-life aerodynamics ! The forces are dynamically adjusted based on airspeed, angle of attack, deformation and braking inputs, allowing for <strong>highly detailed collapses</strong>, <strong>stalls</strong>, and wind interactions. The wings in WaggaSim also adjust their internal pressure affecting how they bend and flex.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058640/extras/BigTipTouch.gif?t=1725272439\" /><br><br><strong>Procedural Wings &amp; Customization</strong><br><strong>Create</strong> and <strong>modify</strong> your own paragliders, speed wings or even kite ! The intuitive wing editor allows you to <strong>design custom wings</strong>, which will behave realistically based on their shape and structure. Learn the intricacies of paragliding by experimenting with different designs and seeing how they perform in various conditions.<br><br><strong>Ground Interaction</strong><br>Perform stunning <strong>foot drags</strong> and perfect your precision with ease ! The pilot model features <strong>semi-ragdoll physics</strong>, allowing for realistic interactions with the terrain.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058640/extras/Beach.gif?t=1725272439\" /><br><br><strong>Perfect for Training and Fun</strong><br>WaggaSim is designed and balanced to be <strong>fun</strong> and <strong>ideal</strong> for realistic <strong>training</strong>.<br>Why WaggaSim ?<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Educational:</strong> Understand the principles of flight and wing behavior through hands-on experience, practice approaches and maneuvers.<br></li><li><strong>Entertaining:</strong> Enjoy the freedom of flight, the physics based interactions and the beautiful landscapes.<br></li><li><strong>Innovative:</strong> Use the wing builder to create and test custom designs, enhancing both fun and learning.</li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3058640?t=1725272439","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3058640?t=1725272439","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058640/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1725272439","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058640/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1725272439","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058640/extras/UltimateFlyingExp.png?t=1725272439\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Experience the Thrill of Flight Like Never Before</h2>WaggaSim is a <strong>realistic paragliding simulator</strong> with advanced <strong>soft-body physics</strong>. The wings and wind-socks behave like <strong>real fabric</strong>, bending and flexing naturally. <strong>Design</strong> or modify your <strong>own gear</strong>, fly and perfect your s