ctice approaches and maneuvers.<br></li><li><strong>Entertaining:</strong> Enjoy the freedom of flight, the physics based interactions and the beautiful landscapes.<br></li><li><strong>Innovative:</strong> Use the wing builder to create and test custom designs, enhancing both fun and learning.</li></ul>","developers":["Gypaete Studio"],"genres":[{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Sports","id":"18"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3058640/header.jpg?t=1725272439","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> glibc 2.17+, 32/64-bit<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core i3 M380<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 MB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> OpenGL 3.0+<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 1000 MB available space</li></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Requires an Apple processor<br></li><li><strong>OS:</strong> Lion 10.7.5, 32/64-bit<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core i3 M380<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> OpenGL 3.0+<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 1000 MB available space</li></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257037754,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257037754/movie480.mp4?t=1720966531","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257037754/movie_max.mp4?t=1720966531"},"name":"WaggaSim - the opening","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257037754/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1720966531","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257037754/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1720966531","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257037754/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1720966531"}}],"nam